'''Bennet Guillory''' is the actor who played [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Qu Rahn/Legends|Qu Rahn]] in the cutscenes of ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]'', credited as "Bennett Gilory" in the game's instruction manual. He also played a [[Memoryalpha:Unnamed Humans (24th century)#Medical big shot|Medical Big Shot]] in [[Memoryalpha:Star Trek|''Star Trek'']] in an episode of [[Memoryalpha:Star Trek: Deep Space Nine|''Deep Space Nine'']] and is thus one of the actors to have appeared in both Star Wars and Star Trek material. He also appeared in two episodes of [[Wikipedia:Babylon 5|''Babylon 5'']].

